265
00:19:53,848 --> 00:19:55,368
No, don't go in there!

266
00:19:55,450 --> 00:19:56,540
Don't go in there!

267
00:20:05,926 --> 00:20:07,396
Don't worry.

268
00:20:09,764 --> 00:20:11,534
I'll talk to him.

269
00:20:12,600 --> 00:20:14,770
He listens to me.

270
00:20:23,010 --> 00:20:24,680
He's not well.

271
00:20:25,713 --> 00:20:27,973
He knows what you're here for.

272
00:20:28,048 --> 00:20:30,608
